stomers' preferences, the\noperational costs can be reduced by up to 5%, whilst customers can save more\nthan 30% in total delivery fees.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Oct 2021 01:58:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 24 Mar 2022 12:46:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-28"}
