 of the Stokes polarization\nvectors and the mean drift bands of the Stokes parameters, is not predicted by\ncurrent theoretical models of pulsar emission. We propose different scenarios\nto explain the generation of the torus, based on either incoherent or\nphase-coherent superposition of orthogonally polarised modes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Oct 2021 05:00:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-05"}
